Package: numhelpr
Title: Helper Functions for Common Number Formatting and Math Tasks
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Zoe", "Doherty", , "dohertyz@lawrence.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides simple helper functions that solve common annoyances when working with numbers in R, including formatting decimals as percentages, calculating percent change, and clamping values within a specified range. 
